    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HOLLOW HOUSE</strong> 是一款第一人称氛围恐怖游戏，故事发生在废弃的房屋和阴森的豪宅中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773130/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.poster.avif?t=1772112384\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773130/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.webm?t=1772112384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773130/extras/80d3039a485b3c1782e0c92760ae7b64.mp4?t=1772112384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索黑暗的房间和狭窄的走廊，与僵尸战斗，寻找武器，并利用光源求生。解开谜题，找到钥匙，打开上锁的门，进入房屋的新区域。危险潜伏在每一扇门后，寂静具有欺骗性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773130/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.poster.avif?t=1772112384\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773130/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.webm?t=1772112384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773130/extras/9c81c9ff203ba6ea9edb583a454633d7.mp4?t=1772112384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个决定都有代价。<br>房子正在注视着你。而你未必能逃脱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773130/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.poster.avif?t=1772112384\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773130/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.webm?t=1772112384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1773130/extras/039c3cd140cc40eec8e7b43f0bad78f6.mp4?t=1772112384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
